ms.safi.btsync.dto

Class FolderPreferences

  • Object
    • ms.safi.btsync.dto.FolderPreferences

  • public class FolderPreferences
extends Object
    JavaBean implementation of a folder's preferences from BitTorrent Sync.

    An example of a folder's preferences: 

     {
      "search_lan":1,
      "use_dht":0,
      "use_hosts":0,
      "use_relay_server":1,
      "use_sync_trash":1,
      "use_tracker":1
 }
    Author:
    Omeed Safi
